parameters.name: 19恋愛パート・恋人との会話

parameters:
Yui: "Thanks to Ginga coming to my rescue, I was able to defeat
Zaida-G."
Ginga: "Gratitude... But I'm glad I made it in time!"
Yui: "By the way, Ginga... how did you know I was Pony-Celes?"

Yui: "Even involving Ginga, geez! I'll have to give her a serious
warning when we get back!"
Ginga: "Of course, I am! It's only natural!"

Yui: "It would be a lie to say I'm not scared, but this is my mission.
I'm okay with it now!"
Ginga: "I want to fight Zaida-G together with Yui!"
Ginga: "Unlike Yui, I haven't been granted any special powers, but..."
Yui: "So you were really scared after all!"

Ginga: "Of course, I am... Just thinking about that monster is
frightening!"
Yui: "But you still came to save me. You were so cool!"

Ginga: "Because Yui is important to me... My body just moved on its
own."
Yui: "...Me too. I like you, Ginga!"
Yui: "Oh come on, this is embarrassing-!"

Ginga: "Ah, you did it now~! And we were having a serious
conversation~"
Ginga splashed water on Yui while blushing.
Yui: "It's payback time! Here you go!"
Yui Ginga (I love you, Ginga) (I love you, Yui)
